headline: Kraft Heinz (NasdaqGS:KHC) Removed From Multiple Russell Indexes
summary: Kraft Heinz (NasdaqGS:KHC) faced a significant change in its index positions with its removal from the Russell Top 200 Index, Russell Top 200 Value Index, and Russell 1000 Dynamic Index, while joining the Russell Midcap and Midcap Value Index. These changes represent a reshuffling of its market classification that could influence investor perception and market exposure.
